.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-balance \- show per-channel balance breakdown
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-balance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns a per-channel balance summary for all channels as a JSON array.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, local_sat, remote_sat, capacity_sat,
  local_ratio, state}]
.fi
Returns an empty array when the daemon is not reachable.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-list (1),
.BR lightning-node-funds (1)
